## What I Can Do

- **Answer Questions**: Ask me anything and I'll provide helpful responses
- **Voice Input**: Speak your questions instead of typing
- **Continuous Conversations**: I remember our conversation context to provide more relevant and coherent responses

## Features

- **Multiple Conversations**: Manage and switch between different chats
- **MCP Integration**: Connect to external tools and data sources
- **Import/Export**: Save and restore your conversation history
- **Themes**: Switch between light and dark modes for comfortable viewing

## Getting Started

Simply type your question in the text box below and press Enter or click the send button (press Shift+Enter to create multi-line messages). You can also click the microphone button to speak your questions instead of typing.